          "process_md": "&amp;amp;amp;amp;gt; **Registration of a Construction Worker under BBOCWWB:**\n\n**Step 1:** Visit the [Official Website](https://bocwscheme.bihar.gov.in/home) of the Bihar Building and Other Construction Workers Welfare Board.\n**Step 2:** On the homepage, click on &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;[Labour Registration](https://bocwscheme.bihar.gov.in/worker_reg)&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;.\n**Step 3:** Enter your Aadhar card number and name, then click &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;Authenticate&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;.\n**Step 4:** A dashboard will appear. Enter all required details, ensuring that all fields marked with an asterisk (*) are filled in correctly.\n**Step 5:** Click on &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;Submit&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot; and proceed to pay the application fee online.\n**Step 6:** You will receive your construction worker registration number upon successful registration.\n&amp;amp;amp;amp;gt; **Apply for Scheme Benefits:**\n\n**Step 1:** Visit the [Official Website](https://bocwscheme.bihar.gov.in/home) of the Bihar Building and Other Construction Workers Welfare Board.\n**Step 2:** Click on &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;Login&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot; and select &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;Labour&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;.\n**Step 3:** Enter your registration number &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp; year of Birth, click &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;Show&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot; to view your details.\n**Step 4:** Select the scheme you wish to apply for to avail the benefits.\n**Step 5:** Enter all required information and upload the necessary documents.\n**Step 6:** Click on &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;Submit Application&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot; to complete the process. \n&amp;amp;amp;amp;gt; **Application Tracking:**\n\nApplicant can track their application status online through the [official website](https://bocwscheme.bihar.gov.in/home) of the Bihar Building and Other Construction Workers Welfare Board. Relevant updates will be sent to the registered mobile number.\n<br>\n\n"
        }
