        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n- The applicant should be a dependent of a deceased worker.\n- The worker, in his/her lifetime, should have been registered with the &quot;Bihar Building &amp; Other Construction Workers Welfare Board&quot;.\n- The worker, in his/her lifetime, should have been in receipt of regular pension from the Board.\n\n",
